research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x)}(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + \u03a3_j \u03b3_j(x) c_j\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d U={u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0cC={c_j} \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u8865\u507f\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + \u5355 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + residual \u8865\u507f\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5148\u7b5b\u6e05\u695a\uff1a`expert_topk` \u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002r79 \u4e0e r80 \u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u628a `STAGE1_RATIO` \u4ece 0.25 \u63d0\u5230 0.5 \u4f1a\u53d8\u5dee\uff0c\u800c\u53bb\u6389 low-rank trunk \u7684 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e5f\u660e\u663e\u5f31\u4e8e matched `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u5230\u4e2d\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u91cc trunk \u4ecd\u662f\u5fc5\u8981\u7ec4\u6210\uff0c\u4e14\u66f4\u5f3a residual cleanup \u6bd4\u66f4\u9ad8 expert-stage \u9884\u7b97\u66f4\u91cd\u8981\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r76 \u4ec5\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 32 \u964d\u5230 24\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u65e2\u7136 routed-only\u3001shared-basis\u3001stage split\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca trunk-free staged \u8def\u7ebf\u90fd\u672a\u5e26\u6765\u66f4\u4f18\u7ed3\u6784\u6bb5\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 `lowrank + expert + residual` \u8fd9\u6761\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5f3a\u517c\u5bb9\u4e3b\u7ebf\u8fd8\u80fd\u5426\u4ec5\u901a\u8fc7\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u7f29\u5fc5\u8981 trunk \u5bbd\u5ea6\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u8d28\u91cf\u7684\u540c\u65f6\u628a total_cost \u518d\u5f80\u5de6\u63a8\u4e00\u5c0f\u6bb5\uff0c\u5e76\u5f62\u6210\u6bd4 r76 \u66f4\u7ecf\u6d4e\u7684\u65b0 Pareto \u70b9\u3002",
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/logs/agent_action_0004.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"A factorized nonlinear encoder may lower FVU at K=128 by adding a hidden mixing stage before latent scoring, giving the encoder more expressive feature composition while keeping the fixed-K decode path unchanged. Test factorized_topk at the same K=128 anchor point as the next quality-first family.","summary":"Both mixture_topk and residual_topk archived under normal runtime with proxy FVU near the topk proxy anchor, so the next move is another architecture family rather than smaller-K search. factorized_topk is the clearest remaining low-friction expressivity upgrade in the current codebase.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is still exploratory, but it continues the right search pattern: hold K fixed, change one architectural idea, and see whether encoder expressivity can move proxy FVU. If this also comes back flat, the current built-in families are not yet showing a path to the target.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"8"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["residual_topk at K=128/ef8/signum archived under normal runtime with proxy FVU 0.3055884689092636, so the residual two-branch prototype did not improve on the anchor.","Round 4 opens factorized_topk as the next expressive family to test at fixed K=128 before considering lower-K or cost-driven moves."],"next_hypotheses":["If factorized_topk improves proxy FVU, follow with a stabilization pass on optimizer or expansion factor before promotion.","If factorized_topk is also flat or worse, shift from parameter-only family swapping to a code edit that introduces a genuinely new encoder family or materially changes one incubating family."]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0114.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":113,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r107-r113 已经证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下形成了真实低成本 Pareto 段，并在 r113 达到约 0.27x / FVU 0.1350。唯一主假设：在 `K=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 固定时，把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，会把 selection cost 从约 0.20x 降到约 0.14x、total_cost 从约 0.27x 左移到约 0.20x，同时若 FVU 仍明显优于当前直接兼容 cost anchor `expert_topk K=128` 的 0.3149，则可以回答“shared+routed 的低成本收益是否真的需要双 routed experts”，并在更低成本带建立新的结构性 anchor。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.20x total_cost 下仍把 FVU 压到约 0.20 或更低，则下一轮应以本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `K`，继续细化这条更便宜的 shared+routed 子线。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显退化而劣于 r113 太多，则说明当前 shared+routed 前沿的质量确实依赖双 routed experts；下一轮不应继续压 active path，而应回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 主线换轴。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 与 r113 接近但成本显著更低，则可判定当前 target 上 shared+routed 的主要收益来自 shared+routed 分解本身，而不完全来自多 routed experts。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 selection cost 自检显示：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的 selection ratio 约 0.14x、deployment ratio 约 0.06x、combined ratio 约 0.20x；对应 r113 baseline (`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 为约 0.27x。","r107-r113 已经把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的 shared+routed 低成本线推到 0.42x→0.27x；当前最有信息量的问题不再是继续线性降 K，而是这条线在更低 encoder 成本下是否仍成立。","本轮不需要代码修改；`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 与 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 wiring 已在历史轮次中稳定生效。"],"self_review":"相对 r113 只改一个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则。之所以不继续沿 `K` 轴外推，是因为 r112→r113 已经连续两轮回答 deployment knee，并且都形成了新非支配点；当前更高信息量的是切换到 active-path 轴，直接比较当前 low-cost shared+routed 前沿对双 routed experts 的依赖程度。该点仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"以 r113 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`K=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，测试 shared+routed 在约 0.20x total_cost 下是否仍能显著优于旧 `expert_topk` 低成本锚点，并回答当前低成本收益是否真的依赖双 routed experts。","touched_files":[]}
