research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/logs/round_0018.patch:27:+    """Encoding architecture: 'topk' | 'gated' | 'jumprelu' | 'group_topk' | 'routed_group_topk' | 'residual_topk' | 'factorized_topk' | 'mixture_topk' | 'hybrid_topk' | 'adaptive_threshold_topk' | 'union_topk' | 'refined_topk'."""
research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:28:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u4e2a\u90bb\u57df\u626b\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0b\u4e00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1a\u5b9e\u73b0\u6700\u5c0f\u53ef\u8fd0\u884c\u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:48:      "\u672c\u8f6e\u8981\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u662f\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f `lowrank + expert + residual` \u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u518d\u95ee\u4e00\u6b21 `expert_topk` \u6216 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 K \u8f74\u659c\u7387\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0171.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family 仍为 `lowrank_expert_topk`。最终重构公式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`：其中 `{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，`{b_{e,i}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子；在线侧只需要计算 trunk 系数 `β_r(x)`、轻量 router 选出少量 expert，再在被选中的静态子库内做有限加权和。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + routed 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。r170 已在 `<0.25x` 主战场上给出一个有价值信号：`lowrank_expert_topk` 在约 `0.24x` total_cost 下做到 `FVU=0.1404`，虽然尚未击败 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=112` 的 `0.1369`，但已明显接近，说明这条“轻 trunk + routed expert、无 residual cleanup”路线并未被证伪。当前最值得回答的单一问题不是继续回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做更低信息量的局部细扫，而是：`lowrank_expert_topk` 能否在更低成本下仍维持对 low-cost anchors 的竞争力。故本轮以 r170 为 reference，只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 压到 `160`，其余 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, adam, LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试更小 per-expert width 是否能把该 family 从约 `0.24x` 压到约 `0.21x`，并在相近或更低成本下挑战当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 `0.20x-0.22x` 前沿段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 仍把 FVU 压在约 `0.145` 以内，则下一轮继续留在 `lowrank_expert_topk`，只改 `K`，定位它在 `0.20x-0.22x` 带内的 deployment knee。","如果该压缩后 FVU 明显退化到被同成本 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors 支配，则可下调 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在当前 target 的优先级，回到别的轻量兼容 family，而不是继续沿这条线细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式是静态 trunk 库加少量 routed 静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性应维持为扩展兼容。","本地 cost 自检显示：相对 r170，把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 降到 `160` 后，`lowrank_expert_topk(K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64)` 的 combined_accesses 约从 `1015808` 降到 `884736`，combined_ratio 约从 `0.24x` 降到 `0.21x`，仍稳居 `<0.25x` 主战场。","r166-r169 已基本说明继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 上做同类小步细扫的信息增量有限；当前更高价值的是验证谁能在更低成本下逼近或击败它。"],"reference_round":170,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：以有效已跑通的 r170 为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。选择这条轴而不是 `TRUNK_RANK`，是因为它带来的 total_cost 下压更明显，能更直接回答 `lowrank_expert_topk` 是否真能在更低成本段形成新前沿；主要风险是 expert width 压缩过头后质量退化，但这正是本轮需要澄清的核心问题。","summary":"以 r170 为 reference，仅将 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 降到 `160`，测试这条扩展兼容的轻 trunk+routed-expert 路线能否把 total_cost 从约 `0.24x` 压到约 `0.21x`，同时仍保持对当前 low-cost `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors 的竞争力。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0149.json:20:    "summary": "\u5efa\u8bae\u4ee5 r148 \u4e3a reference\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`\u3002\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u6b21\u9762\u5411 0.20x \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u590d\u9a8c\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6253\u78e8 `lowrank_expert_*` \u6216 `shared_routed_expert_topk`\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cexpert \u5185 low-rank local head\u201d\u5728\u5f53\u524d 2-expert recipe \u4e0b\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5f62\u6210\u6bd4\u73b0\u6709\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u951a\u70b9\u66f4\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u65b0\u6bb5\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0149.json:43:      "\u82e5\u8be5\u70b9\u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u52a3\u4e8e\u540c\u6210\u672c `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u951a\u70b9\uff0c\u5219\u53ef\u66f4\u660e\u786e\u5730\u4e0b\u8c03 `factorized_expert_topk` \u4ee5\u53ca\u76f8\u5173 expert-internal low-rank \u65e0 shared/residual \u7ebf\u7684\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0149.json:64:    "description": "\u5efa\u8bae\u4ee5 r148 \u4e3a reference\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`\u3002\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u6b21\u9762\u5411 0.20x \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u590d\u9a8c\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6253\u78e8 `lowrank_expert_*` \u6216 `shared_routed_expert_topk`\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cexpert \u5185 low-rank local head\u201d\u5728\u5f53\u524d 2-expert recipe \u4e0b\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5f62\u6210\u6bd4\u73b0\u6709\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u951a\u70b9\u66f4\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u65b0\u6bb5\u3002",
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/session_brief.json:406:        "If mixture_topk is flat or worse under normal runtime, try another expressive family such as residual_topk or factorized_topk at the same K=128 anchor."
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/session_brief.json:429:        "If residual_topk is also flat or worse, try factorized_topk next rather than returning to smaller-K search."
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/session_brief.json:435:    "factorized_topk": {
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/session_brief.json:438:      "design_hypothesis": "The stabilized factorized_topk crash was caused by an implementation bug in the widened hidden-path projection, not by the architecture itself. Fix the hidden-to-latent projection and rerun the same K=128 factorized_topk stabilization pass to recover a valid quality signal.",
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/session_brief.json:467:        "If the fixed factorized_topk now yields a valid proxy improvement, keep incubating the family with quality-focused tuning.",
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/session_brief.json:468:        "If the fixed factorized_topk still performs poorly under normal runtime, stop spending rounds on current built-in families and move to a genuinely new encoder design."
research/history/round_summaries/round_0005.json:20:    "summary": "\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\uff1a`jumprelu` \u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002`factorized_topk` \u5728\u540c\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5df2\u7ecf\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u7ed3\u679c\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5\u5b83\u5fae\u8c03\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u4e0d\u9ad8\uff1b\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u7684\u662f\u6362\u5230\u53e6\u4e00\u4e2a\u540c\u6210\u672c\u3001\u540c\u90e8\u7f72\u5f00\u9500\u3001\u4f46\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 family\u3002\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u4f30\u8ba1\uff0c`jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` \u7684 total_cost \u4ecd\u7ea6 `0.31x`\uff08selection `0.25x` + deployment `0.06x`\uff09\uff0c\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u4f73 `topk@K=64` \u5b8c\u5168\u540c\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u9002\u5408\u505a matched architecture probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0005.json:59:    "description": "\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\uff1a`jumprelu` \u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002`factorized_topk` \u5728\u540c\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5df2\u7ecf\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u7ed3\u679c\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5\u5b83\u5fae\u8c03\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u4e0d\u9ad8\uff1b\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u7684\u662f\u6362\u5230\u53e6\u4e00\u4e2a\u540c\u6210\u672c\u3001\u540c\u90e8\u7f72\u5f00\u9500\u3001\u4f46\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 family\u3002\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u4f30\u8ba1\uff0c`jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` \u7684 total_cost \u4ecd\u7ea6 `0.31x`\uff08selection `0.25x` + deployment `0.06x`\uff09\uff0c\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u4f73 `topk@K=64` \u5b8c\u5168\u540c\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u9002\u5408\u505a matched architecture probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0138.json:25:    "self_review": "\u6ee1\u8db3\u8fd0\u884c\u65f6\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u8ba1\u5212\u8fd0\u884c\u65f6\u76f8\u5bf9 r134 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e0d\u662f\u56de\u5230 `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u6216 `lowrank_expert_*` \u7684\u65e7 family \u5c40\u90e8\u626b\u53c2\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8865\u9f50\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u4f46\u5c1a\u672a\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u201chetero MoE + residual cleanup\u201d\u6700\u5c0f\u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u6539\u52a8\u4e25\u683c\u9650\u5236\u5728 `sparsify/`\uff0c\u5e76\u5df2\u6309 `sae-architecture-integration` \u5b8c\u6210 whitelist\u3001factory dispatch\u3001concrete class \u548c exact architecture smoke\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f residual encoder \u7684 1024x1024 \u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u672c\u8eab\u5c31\u63a5\u8fd1 0.25x\uff0c\u53ef\u80fd\u8ba9\u8be5 family \u7684\u603b\u6210\u672c\u843d\u5728 0.60x \u5de6\u53f3\u5374\u4ecd\u62ff\u4e0d\u5230\u8db3\u591f FVU \u6539\u5584\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6b63\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u9700\u8981\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u8bc1\u636e\u3002",
