research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0151.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"该 matched probe 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。与当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 相比，这个 probe 只移除 soft-codebook coarse branch 与第二阶段 residual refinement，保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与其余主 recipe 不变，因此只回答一个问题：在当前低 EF 预算内，soft-codebook + two-stage 这套更重结构是否真的提供了足够大的质量收益，值得相对 lowrank_residual 更高的 encoder 选择成本与部署查表成本。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_residual 在显著更低 selection_cost 与 deploy 成本下仅小幅损失 FVU，则说明当前主线的复杂结构优势不足以覆盖其总成本，下一轮按规则回到主线后应谨慎继续投入该 family。","若 lowrank_residual 明显更差，则说明不仅第二阶段 refinement 有价值，soft-codebook coarse branch 本身也在 EF=2 下提供了必要结构收益，下一轮回到主线继续做主线 recipe/成本工作。","若 lowrank_residual 终点更差但训练明显更快，则把它记为更便宜的兼容对照点，但不在本轮直接替换主线。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是单次 matched architecture probe，严格只改 architecture，其余 K、EF、optimizer、LR 全部与主线参考配方一致。","lowrank_residual 属于扩展兼容 family，不属于不兼容候选，可合法进入兼容 frontier 对照。","r150 已表明仅去掉第二阶段后的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 仍明显落后于主线；本轮进一步测试若连 soft-codebook coarse branch 一并去掉，性能是否会继续明显下滑。","评估时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分是结构更简单带来的吞吐提升，还是确有更好的总成本-质量权衡。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守本轮架构探针规则：只改 architecture，保持主线的 K、OPTIMIZER、LR、EXPANSION_FACTOR 与主要 recipe 不变。相比更远的 factorized_topk，这个 probe仍沿同一 low-rank residual inheritance line，归因更干净，也更直接回答 soft-codebook coarse branch 本身是否值得继续。","summary":"执行一次严格 matched architecture probe：把当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成更简单的 lowrank_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断 soft-codebook + two-stage 结构相对基础 low-rank residual 是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0249.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"192"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；低秩 factorized scorer 只改变单样本在线侧的打分与选择链路，不改变 decoder 端的单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿导出形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r246 只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`K=96`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试在仍显著低于 plain topk 的总成本下，适度增大低秩 scorer 容量是否能把 `factorized_topk@K96` 的 FVU 从 0.3987 明显压低，从而在约 0.25x 总成本附近补出一枚比 `topk@K32` 更有竞争力的低开销 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_topk@K96,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 明显优于 r246 的 0.3987，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则下一轮继续相对本轮单变量上探到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`，判断这条低秩 scorer 线的质量-成本拐点。","如果质量只小幅改善但运行明显更慢，则把更宽 scorer 记为负面系统信号，不再继续沿 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 上探。","如果即使 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 仍显著差于 `topk@K32` 的 FVU=0.3199，则关闭 factorized scorer 作为 `<0.3x` 主前沿候选，把注意力转回其他低开销 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["r246-r248 已经基本测清 `factorized_topk@FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 K 轴：成本可以极低，但 FVU 始终停在 0.40+，说明当前瓶颈更像 scorer 容量而不是查表预算。","r244 说明默认更宽 hidden_dim 在 `K=96` 下能把 FVU 压到 0.3008，但成本槽位也上移；当前更高信息量的问题是适中的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 能否在低于 topk 左端成本的前提下拿回大部分质量。","本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是质量略好但训练显著更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":246,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r246 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，不联动 architecture、K、EF、optimizer 或 LR。选择回到 `K=96` 并提升 scorer 容量，而不是继续沿 `K` 轴左移，是因为 r246-r248 已经显示低 hidden-dim factorized 线的主要问题是质量而非成本；当前最小、最可归因、也最符合低开销探索目标的动作，是测试适度增宽的 factorized scorer 是否能形成更有价值的 cost-FVU 权衡。","summary":"严格锚定 r246，仅把 `factorized_topk` 的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 96 提到 192，优先验证这条低秩 scorer 线能否在约 0.25x 总成本处显著提升质量，而不是继续扩展已经基本测清的超左端低 K 边界。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0250.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"On the directly compatible `topk` line, increasing `K` from 96 to 160 should produce a materially better `<0.5x` Pareto point, likely around the low-0.18 FVU range at about 0.41x total_cost, while avoiding the recent `factorized_topk` pattern of modest quality gains paired with worse throughput.","summary":"Use `topk` as the next low-cost mainline probe, anchored to r242 and changing only `K` to 160. Final reconstruction formula remains `x_hat = Σ_{i in TopK(x)} α_i(x) b_i`, where all `b_i` come from one static vector library, so this family is `直接兼容` with the LUTurbo/Lottable `查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿` path. This is a strict single-variable step inside the target `<0.5x` region: estimated selection cost stays at the EF=1 topk baseline, deployment lookup rises with `K`, and combined cost should land near 0.41x, filling the gap between the existing 0.38x/0.1968 and 0.44x/0.1635 topk points. Recent `factorized_topk` rounds improved FVU only slightly while increasing runtime cost, so the cleaner frontier-building move is to continue the already monotone-improving topk K ladder.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This is intentionally conservative: it does not open a new family, and it relies on the existing topk trend rather than a new mechanism. The tradeoff is that it will not teach much about new structure, but that is acceptable here because the current priority is to strengthen the `<0.5x` Pareto frontier with a deployable, directly compatible point and to avoid recipes that slow training without a commensurate FVU gain.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Recent `factorized_topk` rounds remained far above the best low-cost topk points, and the wider scorer pass at r249 also reduced throughput to about 111k tok/s, so further factorized widening is currently a weak cost-quality bet.","The EF=1 `topk` K ladder has shown consistent FVU improvement from K=96 to K=128 to K=192 without any compatibility risk; an untested midpoint K=160 is the cleanest next `<0.5x` frontier probe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `topk` K=160 lands near the expected ~0.18 FVU at ~0.41x, test `K=176` next to refine the mid-right edge of the `<0.5x` frontier.","If `topk` K=160 underperforms the monotone trend, shift the next round to a different directly compatible low-cost selector family instead of continuing dense K sweeps.","If runtime regresses disproportionately at K=160, treat that as a system-side warning and prefer lower-cost frontier densification over larger-K topk pushes."],"reference_round":242}
