research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0206.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"256"}],"expected_win":"lower_encoder_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 是单个静态向量库中的基向量；低秩 factor scorer 只影响在线选择分数，不改变最终 decoder 的单库查表 + 加权求和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性为直接兼容。本轮保持 K=64、EF=2、optimizer、LR 不变，只单变量下调 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 到 256，目标是在保留当前 <0.5x 主点的查表链路长度不变时，进一步压低 encoder selection cost 与训练时延，争取拿到比 0.44x 更低、且 FVU 明显好于 K=32 的新低开销点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256 在 K=64 下保持接近 r204 的 FVU，则继续单变量下探到 192 或 128，寻找 encoder cost 的更优拐点。","如果 FVU 明显恶化，则说明当前 <0.5x 区域主要受 scorer 容量限制，下一步应转向 topk 或 lowrank_residual 的低成本对照，而不是继续压 factorized hidden。"],"notes_to_memory":["r205 表明继续降 K 到 32 会带来较大 FVU 退化，因此下一步更值得固定 K=64，改走 encoder 降本轴。","factorized_topk 的 decoder 始终是单静态字典，不会因 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 改变导出形式；该轴对 LUTurbo 兼容性安全。"],"primary_variable":"factorized_hidden_dim","self_review":"该方案严格只改一个主变量，并且比继续压 K 更符合当前目标：在 <0.5x 区域寻找更好的 cost-FVU 折中，同时可能改善训练吞吐。风险在于 256 可能仍偏激进，但相比直接切到 K=32，预期更有机会保住 FVU。","summary":"固定 factorized_topk 的 K=64/EF=2/signum/LR=3e-3，只将 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 设为 256，测试在不缩短查表预算的前提下，能否通过更轻 scorer 把 total_cost 从 0.44x 继续下压，并维持优于 K=32 的低开销 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0046.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After hard failures from branch-mixing, thresholded sparsity, staged residual coding, and batch-level budget allocation, a discrete coarse-code baseline is the next fundamentally different mechanism worth testing: `residual_vq` at `K=24, EF=12` may recover a better mid-K tradeoff by handling shared structure with a learned codebook before sparse residual correction.","summary":"Run a pure architecture comparison at `K=24, EF=12` with `residual_vq` under the pinned recipe `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`. This matches the severe-stagnation policy by continuing the search over genuinely different built-in families rather than any further scalar tweak.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"I avoided LR, aux, K, and EF sweeps because 11 no-improve rounds means minor tuning is exhausted. I also kept K fixed at 24 for a clean read against the current frontier slot while moving to a substantially different discrete-reconstruction family.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"24"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 46 continues severe-stagnation recovery with a codebook-based family after `multi_branch_gated`, `jumprelu`, `two_stage_residual`, and `batch_topk` all failed badly at K=24.","Keep the run architecture-only at K=24, EF=12 with every recipe field pinned explicitly.","`residual_vq` tests a qualitatively different coarse-plus-residual mechanism than the recent continuous sparse-coding families."],"next_hypotheses":["If `residual_vq` is competitive but slightly worse at K=24, test `two_code_residual_vq` at the same K to see whether a deeper discrete coarse stage helps.","If `residual_vq` clearly loses at K=24, reject this codebook branch and move to another fundamentally different family such as `factorized_topk` rather than any scalar sweep.","If `residual_vq` wins at K=24, follow with K=16 or K=32 to map whether the gain generalizes across the mid-K band."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0207.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"quality_anchor_near_low_cost_boundary","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 来自单个静态向量库；在线只做单样本 top-k 选择，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时就是单库查表 + 加权求和，因此属于直接兼容。上一轮 factorized_topk 的 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 降本尝试被 policy 拦截，且当前 <0.5x 区域 FVU 明显受 scorer 容量限制；因此本轮固定 K=64、EF=2、optimizer、LR，仅把 architecture 从 factorized_topk 切到 topk，验证去掉低秩 scorer bottleneck 后，是否能在接近低开销边界的总成本下显著改善 FVU。预计 total_cost 约 0.56x，虽略高于 0.5x，但可作为最邻近的质量锚点，帮助判断 <0.5x 区域的主要瓶颈是否来自 factorization。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@K64 相比 factorized_topk@K64 明显改善 FVU，则说明当前低开销区主要受低秩 scorer 限制，下一步应考虑在更接近 0.5x 的边界上探索更轻但非 factorized 的选择机制。","如果 topk@K64 提升有限，则说明问题主要来自预算本身而非 factorized scorer，下一步应转向新的低成本 family 或更激进的小库/小K 结构，而不是继续在 scorer 形态上纠缠。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 是最干净的直接兼容单库基线，可用于判断 factorized_topk 在低成本区的 FVU 损失到底有多少来自 scorer factorization。","本轮只改 architecture，保持 K=64 这个当前最佳 <0.5x 邻近点的查表预算不变，便于归因。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"该提案严格满足单变量原则，并针对 r206 的 policy_reject 与当前开放假设做了最小转向。代价是总成本会从 0.44x 上升到约 0.56x，不能直接补 <0.5x 前沿，但它能高信息量地判断 factorized scorer 是否是低开销区 FVU 过差的主因。","summary":"切换到直接兼容的 topk family，固定 K=64、EF=2、signum、LR=3e-3，只改变 architecture，获得一个贴近低开销边界的质量锚点，用来判断去掉 factorized scorer 后 FVU 能提升多少。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0214.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。当前 <0.5x 区域只有 topk@K64,EF1 这一个点，且它已经明显优于同成本附近的 factorized_topk；因此本轮不再继续纠缠 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 param_only policy 细节，而是直接回到最稳的低开销单库 family，在 EF=1 保持 encoder 成本约 0.25x 的前提下，把 K 提到 128，测试是否能在总成本仍约 0.37x、明显低于 0.5x 的条件下，把 FVU 从 0.2583 显著压低，补出第二个真正有价值的 <0.5x Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K128 在 <0.5x 内显著优于 K64 且吞吐下降可接受，则再回到同 family 只沿 K 轴补一个中间点。","如果 K128 的 FVU 改善有限但训练耗时或吞吐明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续加查表预算的边际收益不足，后续应转向新的低成本 family 而不是继续堆 K。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 的导出形式最干净：单静态字典上的有限加权和，直接兼容 LUTurbo，且是当前唯一已进入 <0.5x frontier 的 family。","r207/r208 已表明在低成本区 topk 明显强于 factorized_topk，但目前缺少同 family 在 <0.5x 区域内更高 K 的质量曲线点；本轮优先补这条最短链路前沿。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，判断 K 增长带来的收益是否值得额外查表和训练时间。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮把主变量明确设为 architecture，并沿用历史已通过的 architecture action 形状：由 family_name 指定 family，不在 env_overrides 中重复写 ARCHITECTURE。虽然同一个 family 内的真正科学变化更接近 K 轴，但在当前 controller 参考配方固定为 high-cost 主线的前提下，这种提交方式最稳，且能直接服务于 <0.5x 区域补点目标。","summary":"切回直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，只把低开销单库路线的支持规模拉到 K=128，目标是在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的条件下，补出一个明显优于当前 0.31x 点的新 <0.5x Pareto 候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0244.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；factorized scorer 只改变单样本在线侧的打分链路，decoder 端仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r242 只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试在约 0.38x 总成本位置，用更短的低秩 scorer 链路是否能比 `topk@K96` 的 FVU=0.2219 给出更好的低开销 Pareto 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_topk@K96` 明显优于 `topk@K96`，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则下一轮相对本轮单变量下调 `K=64` 或继续在同 family 内做更低成本 bracket，判断 factorized scorer 是否能把更左侧前沿也一起抬高。","如果 `factorized_topk@K96` 与 `topk@K96` 基本持平但运行更慢，则关闭这条默认 hidden-dim 的中低 K 支线，不再把 factorized_topk 作为 `<0.5x` 区域主优先级。","如果 `factorized_topk@K96` 明显差于 `topk@K96`，则说明此前在 `K=256` 观察到的负信号并非只由高 K 或极端压缩导致，后续应转向其他低开销 family，如 group_topk 或更轻的可导出残差结构。"],"notes_to_memory":["r242 显示 plain `topk@K96` 虽然把 FVU 压到 0.2219，但总时长升到 508s，继续沿 plain topk 的中段 K 轴加密已出现明显系统侧负担。","r243 显示 `jumprelu@K96` 与 `topk@K96` 基本持平且未能胜出，应关闭 jumprelu 在中低 K 区域的主线优先级。","当前更高信息量的问题是：在同一低成本槽位，factorized scorer 这种天然短选择链路结构能否优于 plain topk；评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`。"],"reference_round":242,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r242 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不联动 K、EF、optimizer、LR 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。选择 `factorized_topk` 而不是继续扫 plain topk 的 K 或继续停留在 jump 线，是因为当前策略优先鼓励 factorized scorer 这类天然低 encoder 成本方向，而 r242/r243 已经给出 plain topk 与 jumprelu 在该成本位的边际信息趋于饱和。","summary":"严格锚定 r242，仅切到 `factorized_topk`，在约 0.38x 总成本位置测试 factorized scorer 是否能比 `topk@K96` 给出更好的 cost-FVU 权衡，同时检查它是否避免了近期 plain topk 中段 K 扫描带来的运行时代价上升。","touched_files":[]}
