research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0060.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 59 ruled out `factorized_topk` as a strong matched alternative under the current `gated` recipe: at `0.229180` it was clearly too weak, so the next single architecture question should move to a different export-compatible support-formation mechanism rather than another heavier scoring path. `jumprelu` preserves LUTurbo's static-vector finite weighted-sum reconstruction contract while replacing the learned input-conditioned gate with per-latent thresholding, so this round asks one clean yes/no question: under the exact current mainline recipe (`K=128`, `EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`), is `jumprelu` competitive enough in full-curve behavior to justify any later follow-up as a potentially cheaper deployment family?",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0060.json:79:      "Round 59 showed that matched `factorized_topk` is not promising under the strengthened mainline recipe: its `0.229180` endpoint is far from the `gated@128` anchor, so that family should not be prioritized for LUTurbo-oriented follow-up.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0238.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r235 只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003`、`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` 及其余配置不变，测试在超低查表预算下，最短选择链路的单库 topk 是否能在约 0.28x 总成本处显著优于当前左端低成本点 `factorized_topk@0.30x` 的 FVU=0.3909，并补出 `<0.5x` Pareto 前沿左侧缺失的一枚更可用点。选择这一步而不是继续推进 `factorized_topk`、`codebook_topk` 或 `topk@K248` 的 recipe 微调，是因为 r237 已明确否定 factorized scorer 扩容线，r235 已明确否定单 coarse codebook 低成本线，而 r236 也已否定当前最强 topk 锚点的 LR 微调；在这种情况下，回到尚未被干净回答的 `topk@EF1,K32` 左端点，是当前最小、最可解释且最符合 `<0.5x` 主战场目标的动作。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `topk@EF1,K32` 在约 0.28x 成本处明显优于 `factorized_topk@0.30x` 的 FVU=0.3909，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则相对本轮继续单变量上探 `K=48` 或 `K=64`，把左侧低成本前沿补完整。","如果 `topk@K32` 的 FVU 仍接近或差于 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，则说明单库极低 K 区域已进入明显退化区，后续不应再把主注意力放在 `<0.3x` 左端。","如果质量有改善但运行显著更慢，则按运行时优先级将其记为负面系统信号，不把该配方升格为左端前沿点。"],"notes_to_memory":["r235 已确认 `codebook_topk@K32` 在约 0.38x 成本处明显劣于 plain topk 主线，应关闭这条单 coarse codebook 低成本线。","r237 已确认 `factorized_topk@K256,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=384` 仍明显差于同成本 topk，应关闭 factorized_topk 的 FHD 扩容线。","r236 已确认 `topk@K248` 的 LR 下探不是正收益；当前更高信息量的问题不再是 recipe 微调，而是 `<0.3x` 左端是否存在比 factorized scorer 更可用的简单单库点。","评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是轻微质量收益但运行更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":235,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r235 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不联动 K、EF、LR、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA 或任何新参数。主要风险是 `topk@K32` 可能因为 residual 容量过低而只给出一个劣质左端点；但这正是当前 `<0.5x` 区域仍未被干净测到、且对 Pareto 左边界最有信息量的单一问题。","summary":"相对 r235 的 `codebook_topk@EF1,K32` 做一次严格 param_only architecture probe，仅切到 `topk`，验证最简单单库结构能否在约 0.28x 总成本处补出一个优于当前最左端 `factorized_topk` 的低成本 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0238.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u4e0e\u7cfb\u6570\u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u90e8\u7f72\u4fa7\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 reference_round=r235 \u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a env \u53c2\u6570 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=signum`\u3001`LR=0.003`\u3001`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` \u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u7f6e\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5728\u8d85\u4f4e\u67e5\u8868\u9884\u7b97\u4e0b\uff0c\u6700\u77ed\u9009\u62e9\u94fe\u8def\u7684\u5355\u5e93 topk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u7ea6 0.28x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u5904\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d\u5de6\u7aef\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u70b9 `factorized_topk@0.30x` \u7684 FVU=0.3909\uff0c\u5e76\u8865\u51fa `<0.5x` Pareto \u524d\u6cbf\u5de6\u4fa7\u7f3a\u5931\u7684\u4e00\u679a\u66f4\u53ef\u7528\u70b9\u3002\u9009\u62e9\u8fd9\u4e00\u6b65\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u63a8\u8fdb `factorized_topk`\u3001`codebook_topk` \u6216 `topk@K248` \u7684 recipe \u5fae\u8c03\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a r237 \u5df2\u660e\u786e\u5426\u5b9a factorized scorer \u6269\u5bb9\u7ebf\uff0cr235 \u5df2\u660e\u786e\u5426\u5b9a\u5355 coarse codebook \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c r236 \u4e5f\u5df2\u5426\u5b9a\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5f3a topk \u951a\u70b9\u7684 LR \u5fae\u8c03\uff1b\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\uff0c\u56de\u5230\u5c1a\u672a\u88ab\u5e72\u51c0\u56de\u7b54\u7684 `topk@EF1,K32` \u5de6\u7aef\u70b9\uff0c\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5c0f\u3001\u6700\u53ef\u89e3\u91ca\u4e14\u6700\u7b26\u5408 `<0.5x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u52a8\u4f5c\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0238.json:20:    "summary": "\u76f8\u5bf9 r235 \u7684 `codebook_topk@EF1,K32` \u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u4e25\u683c param_only architecture probe\uff0c\u4ec5\u5207\u5230 `topk`\uff0c\u9a8c\u8bc1\u6700\u7b80\u5355\u5355\u5e93\u7ed3\u6784\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u7ea6 0.28x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u5904\u8865\u51fa\u4e00\u4e2a\u4f18\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5de6\u7aef `factorized_topk` \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c Pareto \u70b9\u3002",
