research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0210.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 u_r 是静态 trunk 向量库，b_i 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算系数 beta_r 与 alpha_i，并在 LUTurbo/Lottable 端导出为两个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此属于扩展兼容。r209 对 topk@EF1,K96 的继续加大查表预算被 policy 拦截，说明单纯沿 topk 的 K 轴上探不稳；本轮保持 K=64、EF=1、optimizer、LR 不变，只把 architecture 从 topk 切到 lowrank_factorized_residual，测试在仍瞄准 <0.5x 区域的前提下，加入极轻 low-rank trunk 与 factorized residual scorer 后，是否能显著优于 topk@0.31x 的 FVU。按现有成本表外推，该配置有希望落在低开销区或其边界附近，同时提供比纯单库 topk 更强的表达。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 lowrank_factorized_residual@EF1,K64 成功落入 <0.5x 且明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则下一步固定该 family，单变量扫描 K 或 TRUNK_RANK，补齐低开销前沿。","如果该配置仍超出 <0.5x 或 FVU 改善有限，则说明低开销区需要更短链路而非增加 trunk 分支，下一步应回到 topk/factorized_topk 或探索更小静态库方案。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库加 residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。","本轮只改 architecture，保持 K=64 和 EF=1 不变，便于判断在同等低字典规模与相近 lookup 预算下，增加轻 trunk 是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"该提案遵守单变量原则，并直接回应 r209 的 policy_reject：不再继续沿 topk 的 K 轴加预算，而是测试更有信息量的新低成本 family。主要风险是 deployment 侧 trunk 成本可能把 total_cost 推到 0.5x 附近甚至略上，但这仍能为低开销区提供关键边界信号。","summary":"切换到扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual，固定 K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，只改变 architecture，验证轻量 trunk+residual 结构能否在低开销区附近拿到明显优于 topk 的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0159.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u67b6\u6784\u63a2\u9488\u89c4\u5219\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf architecture\uff0c\u5e76\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u8fdc\u7684 topk \u6216 factorized_topk\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684\u6700\u8fd1\u7236\u8282\u70b9\uff0c\u80fd\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u5730\u9694\u79bb\u201c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9636\u6bb5 residual refinement \u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u8fd8\u80fd\u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u7167\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0159.json:80:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u67b6\u6784\u63a2\u9488\u89c4\u5219\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf architecture\uff0c\u5e76\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u8fdc\u7684 topk \u6216 factorized_topk\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684\u6700\u8fd1\u7236\u8282\u70b9\uff0c\u80fd\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u5730\u9694\u79bb\u201c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9636\u6bb5 residual refinement \u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u8fd8\u80fd\u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u7167\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0161.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 是单样本稀疏系数，因此最终表示是单库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.38x h×n，显著低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x，且满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮严格保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 不变，只将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 factorized_topk，回答唯一问题：这种更激进的低秩单库选择机制在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下是否仍值得继续，还是其表示能力会明显落后于保留 trunk + codebook + staged refinement 的主线结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 factorized_topk 明显落后于当前主线，则说明极低选择成本单库路线在当前 regime 下不值得继续，下一轮回到主线。","若 factorized_topk 与当前主线差距小于预期且运行代价更优，则记录其为更激进低成本备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 factorized_topk 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的系统级成本收益需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["factorized_topk 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为直接兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159-r160 已说明去掉 second stage 和去掉 soft-codebook coarse branch 都会明显恶化；本轮补充检验更低成本的直接兼容单库路线是否还有继续价值。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更低成本或更差质量误判为吞吐波动。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 factorized_topk 而不是再次重复已测过的 topk/lowrank 父节点，是为了用一次更低 selection_cost 的直接兼容 probe 回答当前剩余的关键问题：极低成本单库路线是否还有继续价值。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 factorized_topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断这种更低成本的直接兼容单库架构是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0060.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 59 ruled out `factorized_topk` as a strong matched alternative under the current `gated` recipe: at `0.229180` it was clearly too weak, so the next single architecture question should move to a different export-compatible support-formation mechanism rather than another heavier scoring path. `jumprelu` preserves LUTurbo's static-vector finite weighted-sum reconstruction contract while replacing the learned input-conditioned gate with per-latent thresholding, so this round asks one clean yes/no question: under the exact current mainline recipe (`K=128`, `EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`), is `jumprelu` competitive enough in full-curve behavior to justify any later follow-up as a potentially cheaper deployment family?","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe on `jumprelu`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`, and the same runtime knobs, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `jumprelu`. Judge this probe by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `jumprelu` stays smooth and remains reasonably close to the `0.142923` `gated` anchor, it is worth keeping in reserve because its thresholded support path may reduce LUTurbo online selection overhead versus a full gating branch; if it is clearly worse across the curve, archive it as a non-promising matched alternative and return to the `gated` mainline next round.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the Round 60 matched-probe rule by changing exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, while keeping `K`, `OPTIMIZER`, `LR`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, and the settled mainline recipe fixed. `jumprelu` is a sensible LUTurbo-oriented probe because it preserves the same static library weighted-sum output form while simplifying support shaping relative to `gated`; the main risk is that the matched `gated`-tuned recipe may not be ideal for its threshold dynamics, but that is acceptable for a family-worthiness screen.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"1"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 59 showed that matched `factorized_topk` is not promising under the strengthened mainline recipe: its `0.229180` endpoint is far from the `gated@128` anchor, so that family should not be prioritized for LUTurbo-oriented follow-up.","`jumprelu` remains LUTurbo-compatible because the reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over a static decoder library with fixed `K`; the architectural change is confined to threshold-based support shaping before top-k selection.","Round 60 should judge `jumprelu` purely as a family-worthiness probe against the current `gated@128` anchor: if it is clearly worse or unstable, archive it and return to the `gated` mainline next round; if it is competitive, keep exactly one later follow-up slot available."],"next_hypotheses":["If matched `jumprelu` is clearly worse than the strengthened `gated` anchor, return to the `gated` mainline next round and close this probe.","If matched `jumprelu` is roughly competitive with a healthy curve, still return to the `gated` mainline next round, but preserve one later revisit because its thresholded support path may better align with LUTurbo online-cost goals.","If matched `jumprelu` unexpectedly beats the current `gated` anchor, return to the `gated` mainline next round per policy but schedule exactly one later follow-up for this family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
